purpose: Fetch the EC (Embedded Controller, i.e. KB3700) microcode

command: &builder &this
build-now

macro: EC B73

" wget http://dev.laptop.org/pub/ec/ec_v${EC}.img -O ec.img" expand$ $sh

\ This forces the creation of an ec.log file, so we don't re-fetch ec.img
writing ec.version
" ${EC}"n" expand$  ofd @ fputs
ofd @ fclose
